description: This file defines the Analysis class representing analysis results for resumes or match scoring, annotated as a MongoDB document.

classes.name: Analysis
classes.description: Represents the result of an analysis for resumes or job matches, stored as a MongoDB document.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the unique identifier of the analysis.

methods.name: getType
methods.description: Returns the type of analysis ('resume' or 'match').

methods.name: getScore
methods.description: Returns the score result of the analysis.

methods.name: getDetails
methods.description: Returns additional details about the analysis as a map.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp when the analysis was created.

methods.name: setId
methods.description: Sets the unique identifier of the analysis.

methods.name: setType
methods.description: Sets the type of analysis ('resume' or 'match').

methods.name: setDetails
methods.description: Sets the additional details map for the analysis.

methods.name: setCreatedAt
methods.description: Sets the created timestamp for the analysis.
